The Flash is a 1990 American television series developed by the writing team of Danny Bilson and Paul De Meo that aired on CBS .
It is based on the DC Comics character Barry Allen / Flash , a costumed superhero crime-fighter with the power to move at superhuman speeds .
The Flash starred John Wesley Shipp as Allen , along with Amanda Pays , Alex DÃ©sert , and Paula Marshall .
It was the first-ever live-action portrayal of the DC superhero .